<h1 class="hero-h">2026 B2B AI vendor <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">comparison matrix.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">A side-by-side comparison of the 12 AI vendors mid-market B2B buyers most often evaluate. Built from observation, vendor documentation review, and direct buyer feedback through May 2026. Updated quarterly. Designed for buyers running real evaluations and analysts/journalists who need a citable structured comparison.</p>
